---
title: Smashed Chermoula Bean & Beef Tacos with Slivered Almonds & Garlic Aioli
description: Bursting with paprika, cumin and turmeric, our chermoula spice blend works wonderfully with tomato paste to create a saucy base for the cannellini beans and beef strips. The salad and almonds add extra texture, and the tasty garlic aioli really makes the dish sing.

*Due to local availability, we’ve replaced some of your ingredients. They may be a little different to what’s pictured, but just as delicious!*
